*scim-0.5.1 (07 Jul 2003)

  07 Jul 2003; Alastair Tse <liquidx@gentoo.org> scim-0.4.1.ebuild,
  scim-0.5.1.ebuild, files/scim-0.5.1-gtk2immodule.patch:
